data.description: Seller is offering $10,000 towards Buyers closing costs or rate buy down with a full price offer! Introducing your dream home in highly sought-after Stetson Valley in North Phoenix! This stunning 2-story residence boasts 3 generously sized bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, a massive loft, and a spacious 3-car garage. As you step inside, you'll be greeted by an open and airy floor plan, featuring a well-appointed kitchen with modern appliances and ample counter space. The inviting living room is perfect for relaxing and entertaining, while the formal dining area is perfect for family gatherings. Upstairs, the primary suite is a true retreat with a luxurious en-suite bathroom and a walk-in closet. Two additional bedrooms provide plenty of space for family or guests. The huge loft area can be customized to suit your lifestyle, whether it's a home office, game room or additional living space. Outdoors, the generous backyard offers endless possibilities, with ample space. Recent updates in 2023 include a beautiful kitchen backsplash, stainless steel appliances, reverse osmosis system, water softener and filtration, water heater, new flooring downstairs, and backyard landscaping. WOW!! Don't miss the opportunity to make this exceptional home your own. Stetson Valley is known for its scenic mountain views and easy access to parks, trails, and excellent schools. Experience the best of North Phoenix living in Stetson Valley!
